Description: All Annual Meeting attendees are invited to participate in this special evening session hosted by Drs. Lorelei A. Mucci and Paul A. Scheet, Chairs of the AACR Population Sciences Working Group. The 2024 PSWG Town Hall will feature a panel discussion from experts in the population sciences community on the theme of "Artificial Intelligence for Research Enhancement in Population Sciences." The Town Hall also includes a Networking Reception at the beginning and conclusion of the session.
